@node History "SCopy: History"

 Nov  6 1994 - V1.00 - First release
 Dec  6 1994 - V1.01 - Fixed small bug with files of zero bytes in size
 Dec  8 1994 - V1.02 - Added a extra progress-bar which shows the total
                       bytes copied of all files to copy
               V1.03 - Made the progress window a bit more font-sensitive
               V1.04 - Added Ctrl C breaking
 Feb 20 1995 - V1.05 - Skipped (fake 1.05 SCopy archive)
 Apr 13 1995 - V1.06 - Now correctly handles current directory, which
                       means stuff like 'SCopy C:Dir ""' now works as
                       it should
 Apr 16 1995 - V1.07 - Added Abort gadget; Changed layout a bit
 Apr 23 1995 - V1.08 - Fixed bugs with empty files (files with length 0);
                       Removed bytes copied text and replaced it with a
                       time indication of how long the copy will take to
                       complete

@endnode

